    "slug": "zenodo",
    "name": "Zenodo",
    "emoji": "🔬",
    "tagline": "Search open research datasets and publications",
    "description": "Zenodo (run by CERN) hosts open datasets, papers and software with DOIs. Its API searches and fetches records with metadata, files and citation info — keyless for read access, though a token raises rate limits. A front door to open-science outputs.",
